data.summary: [Business Wire] - Deutsche Bank today announced that it will reduce the redemption unit size on eighteen of its commodity-based Exchange Traded Notes to 100 ETNs on the 15th calendar day of each month .The redemption unit size for the rest of each month will remain the same as set forth in the related pricing supplement.
data.title: Deutsche Bank Reduces the Redemption Size of Eighteen Exchange Traded Notes on a Specified Day of Each Month
